body:
### Description

I am attempting to rotate text by 90-degrees using canvas.DrawTextOnPath - however the vertical font is distorted. What am I missing here?

### Code

        public static byte[] Test()
        {
            var info = new SKImageInfo(100, 100, SKColorType.Rgba8888, SKAlphaType.Opaque);
            var bitmap = new SKBitmap(info);
            var canvas = new SKCanvas(bitmap);
            canvas.Clear(SKColors.White);
            using (var paint = new SKPaint())
            using (var path = new SKPath())
            {
                var text = "TESTING 123";

                paint.TextSize = 14;
                paint.Typeface = SKTypeface.FromFamilyName("Terminal");
                //paint.Typeface = SKTypeface.FromFamilyName("Courier New");
                paint.Color = SKColors.Red;

                //draw horizontal text
                canvas.DrawText(text, 0, 95, paint);

                //draw same text vertically along a path
                path.MoveTo(95, 95);
                path.LineTo(95, 0);
                canvas.DrawTextOnPath(text, path, 0, 0, paint);
            }

            var bytes = bitmap.SaveToBytes(SKEncodedImageFormat.Png);
            //if (System.IO.Directory.Exists("c:/temp"))
            //    System.IO.File.WriteAllBytes("c:/temp/test.png", bytes);
            return bytes;
        }

### Expected Behavior

I would expect the vertical "TESTING 123" text to be 100% identical down to the horizontal version of the text, yet simply displayed vertically.

### Actual Behavior

The vertical font is distorted, with the naked eye you can see the vertical typeface is distorted. I have have attempted to change to different fonts (Terminal, Courier New) and also font sizes and in all attempts the vertical text is messed-up.

### Basic Information

- Version with issue:  1.60.3
- IDE:  Visual Studio
- Platform Target Frameworks: .NET Standard 2.0
- Target Devices:
  -   Windows 10

### Screenshots

![test](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16097639/46803942-464c7780-cd59-11e8-9181-91f61dd7174a.png)

> VS bug [#738685](https://devdiv.visualstudio.com/DevDiv/_workitems/edit/738685)
